channel.title: Looking to join a Team/Project
channel.description:
Hi, I am looking to join a Development Team/Project.
A little about myself - I'll be turning 21 in 23 days, I play Runescape off and on, I like to go for walks, I love being part of a team, and also I like to help out.
What kind of team am I looking for? - An honest, active team. Something with a goal in mind, rather it be Economy based, PvP based, etc.
What Can I offer? Well I'm not the best coder by far, but I do have experience in real life and on RSPS's as a Community Manager.
I'm basically looking for a part of a team that thinks it will go far and to help out with things daily and stuff.
If you're looking for help, add me on Skype at - Garrett3650
